ERRORS/MISCELLANEOUS
--------------------
To get output without needing the ESD or ARTS plugins I created a new
plugin based on the existing irix plugin.
I call it irixold since it supports the old-style audio API from Irix 6.2
and Irix 5.3.
I plan to submit this new plugin upstream once I'm confident that it works
for most cases.
